<H2>What's the deal with the PayPal link?</H2>
<P>
Ok, we'd like to keep GuildMagic running. Better still we'd like to keep adding to the system, making it better and better. But the speed problems are really getting us (and you) down. Here's the deal - we'll agree to provide a new dedicated server to run GuildMagic on if you folks will agree to pay for the bandwidth (the internet connection). That means that we'd like you to consider making a voluntary contribution towards our internet connection costs. We'll basically buy whatever we can afford to on the money you donate. You can contribute whatever you feel is a fair amount by clicking this PayPal button.
<P>
We've attempted to answer some common questions in the rest of this document.
